Taron da Trump ya yi a West Virginia, da tashar YouTube
A Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau, Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wani babban gangamin neman goyon bayan yakin neman zabe.
A mako mai zuwa, Trump zai yi wasu tarurruka guda biyar, da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi da kuma wasu wurare masu kyau.
Tare da dakatar da ƙuri'un da aka tsara a cikin zabensa don nadin mukamin Kotun Koli, Trump yana da niyyar neman taimako don zaɓen tsakiyar zangon da ke tafe saboda yana da haɗarin cewa 'yan Republican za su fita daga ikon majalisa a lokacin ƙididdigar ƙuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya lokacin taron gangamin Trump da za a yi a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma ET.
Za ku iya kallon taron gangamin Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump na iya yin jawabi a zaman sauraron wannan makon da aka yi wa dan takarar da ya yi takarar a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka dakatar da tabbatar da kuri'ar da aka yi tsammani a majalisar dattijai na mako daya, yayin da ake gudanar da binciken FIT, saboda zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata.
Amma, babban burin wannan taro na masu fafutuka shi ne ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaɓe a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, Shugaba Trump ya bayyana a lokacin kamfen din cewa, "waɗannan tarurrukan guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, za su ƙarfafa 'yan'uwa masu ba da kai da masu goyon baya a matsayin ƙoƙarin da 'yan Republican suke yi na kāre da kuma ƙara yawan rinjayen da suka rasa a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Wakilai".
Wani mai magana da yawun Trump da aka cire daga kamfen din ya ce, "Sarrafa majalisa ta zama muhimmiyar hanya a ajandarsu, har shugaban zai ziyarci jihohin da za su yi aiki sosai a lokacin kamfen din. "
Rahoton na yammacin Virginia Metro News, wanda aka shirya a filin wasa na Wesbank Arena a Wheeling, na iya kawo hankalin masu goyon bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania zuwa ga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, za ta zama ta biyu a cikin watan da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a 2016.
A cikin binciken da 'yan Republican na West Virginia suka yi na Majalisar Dattawa, Trump ya yi gaba wajen neman taimakon dan takarar da ya rage, Patrick Morris.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, masanin kimiyyar siyasa Simon Haider na jami'ar West Virginia ya ce, "idan shugaban kasa ya yi kokarin ganin ya sa Morris ya yi nasara a zaben, wannan ba zai yi masa kyau ba".
