HIV/AIDS: Rahotanni sun nuna cewa, an samu karuwar cutar a China da kashi 14 cikin ɗari
China ta sanar da cewa an samu karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da ke fama da cutar HIV da Aids a kasar.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane sama da 820,000 ne ke dauke da cutar a fadin kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu kusan 40,000 na sabbin kamuwa da cutar.
Idan muka yi la'akari da yadda yanayin ya canja a kwanan nan, za mu ga cewa yawancin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar sun kamu da cutar ne ta hanyar jima'i.
A al'adance, cutar kanjamau tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da cutar ta jini.
A wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan, jami'an kiwon lafiya a kasar Sin sun ce adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ta HIV ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da 100,000.
Kamuwa da cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i da al'ummar LGBT ta kasar Sin ke yi babbar matsala ce.
A 1997, an ba da izinin 'yan luwadi a kasar Sin, amma an ce ana nuna wariya sosai ga al'ummar LGBT.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda tsananin ra'ayin al'ada da ake da shi a ƙasar, kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Saboda yawan kamuwa da cuta, a cikin waɗannan dangantaka akwai rashin tsaro game da jima'i.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi kokarin magance wannan matsalar, ta yi alkawarin cewa kowa zai samu maganin cutar kanjamau.
