Jirgin ruwan Jamus ya sake jinkiri
A shekarar 2014 ya kamata a fara aiki da sabbin jiragen ruwan yaki na sojan Jamus don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War da suka lalace, amma saboda tsarin da ba daidai ba da kuma tsadar tsada, ba zai yiwu ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa, a cewar kafofin yada labarai na cikin gida.
A cewar wani mai magana da yawun soji, in ji jaridar Die Zeit, an dage aikin jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz, wanda shi ne babban jirgin ruwan sabon jirgin ruwan yaki na Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya shigar da jirgin cikin 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan bayarwa sun shafi makomar babban aikin.
Rundunar sojan ruwa ta ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg guda hudu a shekarar 2007 don maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen-class da ke fama da rauni.
An yi imanin cewa za su samar da makamai masu karfi, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohin da ba a iya gani ba kamar ƙananan radar, infrared da kuma ɓoyewar sauti.
Sauran mahimman fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - yana yiwuwa a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa daga tashar jiragen ruwa na cikin gida har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, ci gaba da jinkiri yana nufin cewa manyan jiragen ruwa na zamani - wanda zai ba Jamus damar yin amfani da wutar lantarki a ƙasashen waje - za su zama marasa amfani har sai sun shiga cikin sabis, in ji Dai Zhen.
Jirgin saman F125 mai tsananin gaske ya yi ta samun sanarwa a bara, lokacin da sojojin ruwan Jamus suka ƙi amincewa da jirgin, suka mayar da shi zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm da Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta mayar da jirgin ruwa ga masana'anta bayan an kai shi.
Ba mutane da yawa suka san dalilan da suka sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ba da labarin "kuskuren software da na'urori" da yawa da ke sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani yayin da aka tura shi yaƙi.
Rashin software ya fi muhimmanci, musamman ma idan aka yi la'akari da cewa jiragen ruwa na Baden - Wurttemberg za su yi amfani da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa guda 120 - rabin ma'aikatan jirgin ruwan da aka saba amfani da shi a cikin jirgin ruwan Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da rundunar ke da shi na ƙarawa a nan gaba.
"Rhineland - Pfalz" mai nauyin ton 7,000 ya yi nauyi sau biyu na jirgin ruwa na wannan rukuni da aka yi amfani da shi a Jamus a Yaƙin Duniya na II.
Baya ga kayan aikin da ba daidai ba, farashin farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - yana zama batun.
An ce ya kai €3.2 biliyan ($3.6bn) daga €2.2 biliyan na farko.
Matsalar sabbin jiragen ruwa, wanda ya zama mai mahimmanci a cikin haske game da gargaɗin da aka yi kwanan nan, yana daɗa rage ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans - Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus ya ce "aikin jirgin ruwa na Jamus yana raguwa".
Jami'in ya ce, a tsawon lokaci, wannan batun ya zama mai tsanani, saboda an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa daga amfani, amma ba a samar da wani jirgin ruwa ba.
Ya ce babu wani jirgin yaki da ya isa ya shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa na Baden-Wurttemberg.
