Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi ikirarin cewa Sanders bai yi wata magana da manema labarai a fadar White House ba tun daga ranar 10 ga Satumba.
Mai watsa shiri Chris Wallace ya tambayi dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ya ce rashin yin bayani ba ya haifar da rashin jin daɗi ga masu ba da labarai na talabijin, ko da yake ya ce: "Ba na jayayya da gaskiyar cewa suna da kyau".
Ta kuma ba da shawarar ƙara hulɗa tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
Ya ce, "Shugaban kasa yana yin tambayoyi fiye da kowane shugaba", ba tare da ambaton hujjoji ba, ya ce, "Mun ga waɗannan lambobin".
Za a ci gaba da gabatar da rahotanni, in ji Sanders, amma "idan 'yan jarida sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, ya fi kyau fiye da yin magana da ni.
