An yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonisiya
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a garin Indonesiya a ranar Juma'a kuma ana sa ran adadin ya karu, in ji jami'ai.
Bayan an katse hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala, yankin arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A garin Palu, an ceto mutane fiye da 16,000 da suka tsira daga bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Dongala, tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 da aka kiyasta a shekara ta 2017, yana kan gabar gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi a bakin wani kunkuntar bakin teku.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami suka auku.
Donggala shi ne reshen da ke bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ya kai fiye da kilomita 300 (180 mi).
Da ke ƙasa da lardin gudanarwa, lardin yana da kimanin yawan mutane 299, wanda ya karu daga 200 a shekara ta 2017.
Fishing da noma ne tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman a yankunan bakin teku na Dongala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma sun fi mai da hankali ne a Morovaly a gabar ruwan da ke gaba da Sulawesi.
A cewar hukumar bada agajin bala'i ta Indonesia, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya taba shiga yankin Palau da Donggala.
A 1938, tsunami a Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya hallaka mutane tara a Yammacin Dongola.
Indonesia tana zaune a cikin Pacific Ring of Fire a yanayin girgizar ƙasa kuma girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta haifar da tsunami a cikin kasashe 14 a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Akure na Indonesia a Arewacin Sumatra, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, rabi daga cikinsu suna Akure.
2005: Jerin girgizar kasa mai karfi ya afkawa gabar tekun yamma na Sumatra a watan Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: An yi girgizar ruwa mai karfin awo 6.8 a tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai a gabar Sumatra, inda tsunami mai karfin mita 10 ya lalata kauyuka da dama, kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai saurin ruwa a Akwa ta afkawa yankin Pidi Jaya, ta haifar da lalacewa da kuma rikici saboda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan karon babu tsunami, amma faɗuwar gine-gine ta kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta lalata tsibirin Lompoc na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine - gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido su zama marasa taimako na ɗan lokaci.
